{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-blog-post-js","path":"/docker-in-my-WSL/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"install-docker\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#install-docker\" aria-label=\"install docker permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install <a href=\"https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/ubuntu/\">Docker</a></h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-jsbash\"><code class=\"language-jsbash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> update\r\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> remove <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-y</span> gpg\r\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-y</span> gnupg1\r\n<span class=\"token function\">curl</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-fsSL</span> https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> apt-key <span class=\"token function\">add</span> -\r\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> apt-key fingerprint 0EBFCD88\r\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> software-properties-common <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-y</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> add-apt-repository <span class=\"token string\">\"deb [arch=amd64] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>lsb_release <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-cs</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span> stable\"</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-y</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"after-install-docker\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#after-install-docker\" aria-label=\"after install docker permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>After install Docker</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/linux-postinstall/\">Ref</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-jsbash\"><code class=\"language-jsbash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">groupadd</span> <span class=\"token function\">docker</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">usermod</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-aG</span> <span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token environment constant\">$USER</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Logout</span>\r\nnewgrp <span class=\"token function\">docker</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> systemctl <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">enable</span> <span class=\"token function\">docker</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"wsl-case\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#wsl-case\" aria-label=\"wsl case permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>WSL case</h3>\n<p><em>The <a href=\"https://nickjanetakis.com/blog/setting-up-docker-for-windows-and-wsl-to-work-flawlessly\">WSL1 can use a Docker</a> also but I would choose to use WSL2</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://scotch.io/bar-talk/trying-the-new-wsl-2-its-fast-windows-subsystem-for-linux\">WSL</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/wsl/wsl2-kernel\">Update WSL1 to WSL2</a></li>\n<li>If you failed to install kernal, just remove and reinstall it. (<a href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/WSL/issues/5014\">Ref</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"running\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#running\" aria-label=\"running permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Running</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-jstext\">sudo docker run hello-world</code></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Docker in my WSL","date":"August 18, 2020","spoiler":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/docker-in-my-WSL/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"],"slicesMap":{}}